code: // Returns true if the value matches the predicate protected final boolean contains(long value) {     return Math.floorMod(value, max) == id. }

@Override public boolean equals(Object o) {     if (sameClassAs(o) == false) {         return false.     }     SliceQuery that = (SliceQuery) o.     return field.equals(that.field) && id == that.id && max == that.max. }
@Override public int hashCode() {     return Objects.hash(classHash(), field, id, max). }
@Override public String toString(String f) {     return getClass().getSimpleName() + "[field=" + field + ", id=" + id + ", max=" + max + "]". }
